text: Adeline Sacré (born 12 March 1998 in Saint-Jean-d'Angély) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. and 2016 Women's European Water Polo Championship. == References == == Other websites == * "Adeline Sacre Photos Photos: Budapest 2017 FINA World Championship - Day 5".
